de.feig.FEDM.Core

Class IBrmTableGroup.BrmTableItem

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.feig.FEDM.Core.IBrmTableGroup.BrmTableItem
  • Enclosing class:
    IBrmTableGroup

    public final class IBrmTableGroup.BrmTableItem
extends java.lang.Object
    Class represents one record of requested Buffered Read Mode data with command [0x22] Read Buffer or with received Notification data.
    Description:
    Table class.
    This table collects all data elements, when the reader works in the Buffered Read Mode or Notification-Mode.
